{"id":221,"date":"2017-07-25T16:47:42","date_gmt":"2017-07-25T16:47:42","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=221"},"modified":"2023-11-19T05:14:38","modified_gmt":"2023-11-19T05:14:38","slug":"architectural-drawing","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/general-contracting\/architectural-drawing\/","title":{"rendered":"Architectural Drawing"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e5589d6ba7\" data-id=\"685e5589d6ba7\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\">Hood Builder employs some of the leading architectural draftsmen and design specialists working today. For over 25 years, we have been providing clients of all sizes and in a variety of industries with CAD drafting services for every phase of the construction process.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e5589d6bbd\" data-id=\"685e5589d6bbd\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e5589d6bc9\" data-id=\"685e5589d6bc9\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4>Architectural Drawing\/Drafting Services<\/h4>\n<p>Hood Builder employs some of the leading architectural draftsmen and design specialists working today. For over 25 years, we have been providing clients of all sizes and in a variety of industries with CAD drafting services for every phase of the construction process.<\/p>\n<p>Our architectural draft team has the in-depth knowledge, resources, and talent to take on any construction challenge. We have worked with companies around the country to digitize their building plans and drawings. We can work with any file format and can handle raster and vector conversions, as well as provide dimensioning services.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>CAD Drafting (hard copy drawing or CAD files)<\/li>\n<li>Conversion from hard copy to electronic file<\/li>\n<li>ADA accessibility consulting<\/li>\n<li>Construction consulting<\/li>\n<li>Create, draft or edit CAD drawings<\/li>\n<li>Drawing quality control<\/li>\n<li>Archiving projects at project completion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Expert Drafting at Competitive Pricing<\/h4>\n<p>Many of our clients are surprised to learn of our pricing after spending huge sums of money on architectural services and drafting services in the past. Our expert architectural draft team can help you reduce or eliminate costs while improving productivity.<\/p>\n<p>We understand that your project is unique and important. We will help you realize your business goals by delivering to you the quality drawings you need to bring your architectural vision to life. Our draftsmen and designers will exceed your expectations by delivering a quality product every time.<\/p>\n<h4>Get Expert Drafting Services for Any Sized Project<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New Building Construction<\/li>\n<li>Building Add-Ons<\/li>\n<li>Large-Scale Renovations<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Like our other clients, you will come to prefer us for our competitive pricing, quality services, and the fact that you can turn to us for all your architectural drawing\/drafting needs.<\/p>\n<p><strong>For a full and fast price quote, contact Hood Builder today at <a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\">303-777-7720<\/a>.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;12&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"\/services\/restaurant-services\/\" title=\"Restaurant Services\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-985231\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Restaurant Services<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/\" title=\"Fire Protection\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-876920\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Fire Protection<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n     